{
  "info": {
    "name": "Club Internet Access API",
    "description": "Vente de tickets Wi‑Fi (import CSV Mikhmon) — auth, tickets, paiements, dashboard, utilisateurs.\n\nVariables : `baseUrl` (ex. http://localhost:4000), `token` (rempli après Login). Optionnel : `userId`, `paymentId`, `ticketId`, `typeId`, `transactionId`, `paymentWebhookSecret` (= `TICKETS_PAYMENT_WEBHOOK_SECRET` pour la requête **Webhook Payment**).\n\n**Dashboard** : `GET /api/dashboard/stats` (admin/agent) — `users.byRole`, `tickets.byTicketType`, `recent.users`, `recent.tickets`.\n\n**Keccel direct** : `keccelMerchantCode`, `keccelToken` (Bearer = `KELPAY_TOKEN`), `kelpayTransactionId` (id transaction Kelpay, ex. retour initiate).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4000" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ticketId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "typeId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "transactionId", "value": "MTN123456" },
    { "key": "merchantReference", "value": "" },
    { "key": "keccelMerchantCode", "value": "" },
    { "key": "keccelToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "kelpayTransactionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "paymentWebhookSecret", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Keccel (direct — sans backend)",
      "description": "Requêtes JSON vers **https://pay.keccel.com** (hors API Club). Remplir les variables de collection : `keccelMerchantCode` (= `KELPAY_MERCHANT_CODE`), `keccelToken` (= `KELPAY_TOKEN`, Bearer), `kelpayTransactionId` (champ `transactionId` renvoyé par Kelpay à l’initiation). Si vous utilisez **Basic** au lieu du Bearer : onglet Authorization Postman → Basic Auth, ou en-tête `Authorization: Basic …` à la place du Bearer.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Check transaction (checktransaction.asp)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{keccelToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"merchantcode\": \"{{keccelMerchantCode}}\",\n  \"transactionid\": \"{{kelpayTransactionId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "https://pay.keccel.com/kelpay/v1/checktransaction.asp"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "App",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Root",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register request (code email)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@student.unikin.cd\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Jean\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Test\",\n  \"phone\": \"+243900000000\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/request"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register verify (JWT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access_token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@student.unikin.cd\",\n  \"code\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/verify"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register resend code",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@student.unikin.cd\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/resend"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
